window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Tolkien meets <i>Shock and Awe</i> </p> <p>Orcs. Trolls. Wraith riders. Dark wizards. Together, they form an unstoppable force. Or so they thought. </p> <p><b>Dark Army...meet the US Army Rangers.</b> </p> <p>When a Joint Task Force of elite Rangers are transported to a strange and fantastic future where science and evolution have incarnated the evils of myth and legend, they find themselves surrounded, pinned down, and in a desperate fight for their very survival - against nightmares of flesh and blood made real. Which means only one thing. </p> <p>It’s time to Ranger up and stack bodies. </p> <p>The forces of evil have no idea how dangerous a Ranger has been trained to be, and once the action starts, it won’t let up in this no-holds-barred, full-auto, epic battle for survival in the Forgotten Ruin. </p> <p><i>From the creators of Galaxy's Edge....</i></p> <p><b>Buy in, and jock up for this thrilling WarGate adventure. A battle unlike any other is calling.</b> </p>"; 
